          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The joint analysis of data for total  (gamma,xn)  and",
                " partial    (gamma,n),(gamma,2n)    and    (gamma,3n)",
                " reactions  obtained  in  various   experiments   was",
                " carried   out.  The  new  approach  to  analysis  of",
                " systematic disagreements between data  was  proposed",
                " on   the   base   of   new  criteria  of  systematic",
                " uncertainties   presence   -   specially    proposed",
                " transitional multiplicity functions",
                "        Fi-theor =   SIG(gamma,in)/SIG(gamma,xn).",
                " Using these functions calculated  in  the  frame  of",
                " combined  photonuclear  reaction  model new reliable",
                " and  free  from  problems  of  neutron  multiplicity",
                " sorting  data  for  photoneutron  partial  reactions",
                " cross sections",
                "   SIG-eval(gamma,in) = Fi-theor x SIG-exp(gamma,xn)",
                " were  evaluated  using   experimental  neutron yield",
                " reaction cross sections SIG-exp(gamma,xn)."
              ]
            }
          ],
